{"tid":2044784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[亮劍了]  美制裁港版國安法後  中國首波報復來了…..","createTime":"2020-05-31T10:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T10:54:28.000Z","uid":183058,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0b2f600e30d3651be36cd85ffb9e5346d88855","tid":2044784,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:28:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>美制裁港版國安法後 中國的首波報復來了&hellip;..<br />\n<br />\n中國商務部三十日上午公布，對歐盟美國進口的四氯乙烯繼續課徵反傾銷稅，為期五年，這樣舉動不禁被外界視為，中國已開始反擊美方的制裁行動。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cea7b06c1ec44f2968035d0c71fa314f063adb","tid":2044784,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:29:56.000Z","msg":"不如狗肉加關稅"},{"pid":"620fe2c3808a15c61f76236d8a61cd7a741df6e3","tid":2044784,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"即係乜鳩嘢嚟？"},{"pid":"5addf239d283ada5d6d562175d4888c2e00d25fa","tid":2044784,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7477a2d317ffd3b51232c89703e144cdfa4b0e25","tid":2044784,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:31:56.000Z","msg":"Source 呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba61ba8e1f6c6942ea34e56b88c0ceb7d44cbac","tid":2044784,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"620fe2c3808a15c61f76236d8a61cd7a741df6e3","tid":2044784,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"即係乜鳩嘢嚟？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:32:31.000Z","msg":"乾洗溶劑<br />\n玩自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692d5b6211eef7a958f0fd5314e5e7083dfeda4b","tid":2044784,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"620fe2c3808a15c61f76236d8a61cd7a741df6e3","tid":2044784,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"即係乜鳩嘢嚟？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"四氯乙烯的毒性介於中與低之間。即使四氯乙烯在乾洗與去油被廣泛使用，人類受傷的報告並不常見。[1]然而，國際癌症研究機構已將其列入國際癌症研究機構二A類致癌物。和許多有機氯化合物一樣，四氯乙烯能壓抑中樞神經系統，而四氯乙烯能透過皮膚接觸和吸入蒸氣進入人體[2]。<br />\n<br />\n由於四氯乙烯的毒性與致癌風險，加州空氣資源局（英語：California Air Resources Board）已在2007年禁止新的乾洗機使用四氯乙烯，而舊的乾洗機亦需在2010年中前關掉，並期望在2023年前所有使用四氯乙烯的乾洗機將消失[3] 。<br />\n<br />\n在超過315 &deg;C（599 &deg;F）的環境，例如銲接，四氯乙烯會氧化為光氣，一種劇毒的氣體[4] [5]。<br />\n<br />\nFrom Wiki"},{"pid":"adb780b76bd26d983900517b051cec1d29d13835","tid":2044784,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7477a2d317ffd3b51232c89703e144cdfa4b0e25","tid":2044784,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:31:56.000Z","msg":"Source 呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:33:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200530/OSBN6IO5RNKUMJX2WXYOZDCTNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200530%2FOSBN6IO5RNKUMJX2WXYOZDCTNI%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=c60610b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200530%2FOSBN6IO5RNKUMJX2WXYOZDCTNI%2F&h=eb42243d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200530/OSBN6IO5RNKUMJX2WXYOZDCTNI/</a>"},{"pid":"bc1dc458456599427dea4c4e5bc694f4fa5dfbd3","tid":2044784,"uid":52609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hpcyNL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hpcyNL.gif&h=7f51b689&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"141d91472bd656c77da0c5f3cdcf2b1113d47380","tid":2044784,"uid":183058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"這是中國繼3天前宣佈對美國和歐盟進口的苯酚採取反傾銷措施、5月初對美國和歐盟的無縫鋼管維持徵收反傾銷稅後，又一次祭出「反傾銷」關稅懲罰，延燒中美貿易戰火。<br />\n<br />\n而美國也不甘示弱，美國商務部29日公佈，將對中國進口的不銹鋼啤酒桶及床褥，分別徵收79.7%及1,731%的反傾銷稅。<br />\n<br />\n四氯乙烯被廣泛應用於工業金屬表面油脂去除和乾洗溶劑，尤其衣物乾洗劑、新型環保製冷劑的主要原料，中國是全球最大的石油溶劑進口國。"},{"pid":"e07964c4354947083e74235494eda84c73372611","tid":2044784,"uid":438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:38:10.000Z","msg":"特登講到D垃圾個名好似好把炮<br />\n班冇學識既低下階層就會以為好疊馬"},{"pid":"590cc0fb5882a9cec278d41bdce245f8956b1cac","tid":2044784,"uid":102476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e07964c4354947083e74235494eda84c73372611","tid":2044784,"uid":438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:38:10.000Z","msg":"特登講到D垃圾個名好似好把炮<br />\n班冇學識既低下階層就會以為好疊馬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"氧化二氫"},{"pid":"f1cb161c8d46d2b3a51f261362f910ee86daab54","tid":2044784,"uid":47259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"692d5b6211eef7a958f0fd5314e5e7083dfeda4b","tid":2044784,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"620fe2c3808a15c61f76236d8a61cd7a741df6e3","tid":2044784,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"即係乜鳩嘢嚟？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"四氯乙烯的毒性介於中與低之間。即使四氯乙烯在乾洗與去油被廣泛使用，人類受傷的報告並不常見。[1]然而，國際癌症研究機構已將其列入國際癌症研究機構二A類致癌物。和許多有機氯化合物一樣，四氯乙烯能壓抑中樞神經系統，而四氯乙烯能透過皮膚接觸和吸入蒸氣進入人體[2]。<br />\n<br />\n由於四氯乙烯的毒性與致癌風險，加州空氣資源局（英語：California Air Resources Board）已在2007年禁止新的乾洗機使用四氯乙烯，而舊的乾洗機亦需在2010年中前關掉，並期望在2023年前所有使用四氯乙烯的乾洗機將消失[3] 。<br />\n<br />\n在超過315 &deg;C（599 &deg;F）的環境，例如銲接，四氯乙烯會氧化為光氣，一種劇毒的氣體[4] [5]。<br />\n<br />\nFrom Wiki"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:47:25.000Z","msg":"即係支那仲用致癌物洗衫鬥平做爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac72a74dc3bf978b8f2eb7d055de10c5b6b1bae6","tid":2044784,"uid":357936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc